<div class="changelog-container">
    <header class="changelog-header">
        <h1>Jukebar Changelog</h1>
        <p>Track all the latest updates, fixes, and improvements</p>
    </header>

    <section class="version-block">
        <div class="version-header">
            <h2>v2.0</h2>
            <span class="release-date">03/26/26</span>
        </div>
        <div class="changes">
            <h3>What's new?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Brand new player UI with redesigned circular control buttons</li>
                <li>Playlists are now available directly in the player sidebar</li>
                <li>Skip Shields now work on the currently playing track</li>
                <li>Buttons are disabled when no song is playing to prevent errors</li>
                <li>Leaderboard now has a rolling 7-day reset meaning you songs played within the last seven days are what is tracked</li>
                <li>Your recently queued are now shown when you dont have anything searched in the text box (be careful with this one it can show the songs that were queued as anonymous)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>